# Salienture application (`app/`)

- Laravel 13, PHP 8.3+, Inertia 3, React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind 4.
- Auth: Laravel Fortify → Inertia pages in `resources/js/Pages/Auth/`.
- Pages: `resources/js/Pages/`; UI: `resources/js/components/ui/` (shadcn/Radix).
- Shared props: `HandleInertiaRequests` middleware.
- Tests: Pest in `tests/Feature/` and `tests/Unit/`.
- Run: `composer dev`, `composer test`, `composer lint` from `app/`, or `make test` from workspace root.

Do not add API-only routes unless requested — default is Inertia responses.
